Tool
    - IntelliJ IDEA 2017.14
    - POST MAN
    - Java Play Framework 2.5
    - Google Chrome
    - sbt The interactive build tool
    - Lightbend Activator

SET UP

    - Download project in github https://github.com/chantachet/RestfulWebService

How to Run Project
    1. run with sbt
        - open Command Prompt in project folder
        - sbt run
    2. run with activator
        - open Command Prompt in project folder
        - activator run
    3. run with IntelliJ IDEA
        - Import project to IntelliJ IDEA
        - Select Menu Run -> Edit Configurations
                      -> +
                      -> Select SBT Task
                      -> fill run in Tasks
                      -> Apply
                      -> OK
         - Click Run Project
    4. open http://localhost:9000/ in Google Chrome
    5. Click "Apply this script now!" to create Database
    6. finish setup
    7. Run API with POST MAN